<p class="articletitle"><font color="#000080">Job Search Plus</font></p>

<p>Looking for work is a full-time job in and of itself.&nbsp; You're constantly looking 
for new  opportunities, making contact with companies and 
collecting  information from recruiters and hiring managers.&nbsp; 
Then there are the follow-up calls, applications, interviews, thank you letters, 
more follow-ups by e-mail and phone and the final decisions on each job.&nbsp; <br /><br />


