<i>Job Search Plus</i> is a personal job search organizer that enables you to 
manage all of this information with one easy to use program.&nbsp; With this 
tool, you can maintain complete detail on each lead and have it all 
instantly available at the click of a mouse or offline through one of 
the available reports.&nbsp; Never lose track of an opportunity again or be at a 
loss for the information you need on an interview with this <b>free</b> software.<p><i>
        <a href="jsmanual.htm" 
            title="Click to download your free copy of Job Search Plus.">Job Search Plus</a></i> has been designed for your convenience.&nbsp; 
Features include ...</p>



<ul>
  <li><i>Fast and easy access to specific leads</i> with full indexing and sorting of 
  entries.&nbsp; Search for and view all information on specific opportunities 
  by company, date, last activity and more.</li>
  <li><i>Central management of job details.</i>&nbsp; Instantly access all 
  information related to a specific opportunity including company and&nbsp; contact 
  information, activity history and follow-up reminders.</li>
  <li><i>Storage of attachments</i> related to each lead including e-mails, 
  correspondence and electronic applications for easy viewing.</li>
  <li><i>Detail and summary reports</i> based on active status, location, date and 
  more.</li>
  <li><i>Fast entry of new job leads</i> with the ability to add new information as 
  it's acquired.</li>
</ul>

<p>Job Search Plus offers efficient organization of all the information 
you need to successfully pursue  valuable opportunities.</p>



